dataset.title: Cynanchum neoleucanthum (Apocynaceae), a replacement name for the later illegitimate homonym Cynanchum leucanthum (K. Schum.) K. Schum

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Zhang, Cai-Fei, Onjalalaina, Uy. E., Liao, Miao, Hu, Guang-Wan (2023): Cynanchum neoleucanthum (Apocynaceae), a replacement name for the later illegitimate homonym Cynanchum leucanthum (K. Schum.) K. Schum. Phytotaxa 597 (4): 297-298, DOI: 10.11646/phytotaxa.597.4.5, URL: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/phytotaxa.597.4.5
